{"tid":300320,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"女朋友成日好夜先訓究竟有乜做","createTime":"2017-06-27T20:02:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-28T22:40:56.000Z","uid":125450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"623370fc65417ca78125d38419c1ddff2157618d","tid":300320,"uid":125450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:02:23.000Z","msg":"近依個月發現女朋友成日遲遲都味訓<br />\n因為反緊夜晚看更，成日凌晨見佢仲on 緊wts...最無奈嘅係明明幾個鐘前先wts同我講話我好眼訓唔想傾...<br />\n唉同埋佢冷淡左..有時問佢邊日得唔得閒想見下，佢就會話要練舞又乘又話好眼訓之類，就算出左黎又會話好熱想反屋企...<br />\n<br />\n其實佢係咪識左第二個？我好鐘意佢，唔知點攪好.問佢做咩咁夜都唔訓，佢就話訓唔著...我頭都大q埋！究竟佢係真定假眼訓？真心唔明女仔咁夜訓會係做緊乜？"},{"pid":"c8b4e87a964725b9f8487b77f204d31783b3fa5e","tid":300320,"uid":31746,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:03:27.000Z","msg":"帽"},{"pid":"b653a1ee2e8b58e90957eea0d3e80792ba8f6fb4","tid":300320,"uid":96388,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:09:43.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\">帽事</span>"},{"pid":"77a094a7e324e1325c45fc8210d5e63cc06ee846","tid":300320,"uid":33009,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:11:21.000Z","msg":"[<span style=\"color: green;\">同人傾緊計咪hea覆你同埋好晏都在線囉</span>"},{"pid":"f6c3e24b584c86b87e6e8c3f19d21ac20c799683","tid":300320,"uid":20809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:19:26.000Z","msg":"明知你返夜，都唔隱藏上線時間，咁擺明俾你睇到<br />\n<br />\n分手啦"},{"pid":"c950f10a5cf0f101d0e6080fb1fe1e8e3934eced","tid":300320,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T20:22:39.000Z","msg":"做愛姐"},{"pid":"9e256d0dd5c91507409e15058d6e59703f0ecd5d","tid":300320,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T21:00:16.000Z","msg":"學普通話"},{"pid":"215ddaaf80f0a0d84bf5fb65d7cd7c03a00fa34a","tid":300320,"uid":94005,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-27T22:35:57.000Z","msg":"肯撚定同第二條仔傾得好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  以前個ex都係咁